	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />NESst saves 24-bit BMPs because it was easier to do that way. It draws graphics as 24-bit because besides the graphics itself there are extra things like selection rectangle, grids, etc.
<br />
<br />I can make export 4-bit, it would only require some additional code.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


